Text:
so...crazyjay...did you download it?  it was real, wasn't it?  It was in Italian...WASN'T IT?!?  You asked questions, I answered....the "moron" crack was because you didn't READ before you asked questions.  I should have described your actions as "ignorant".

I don't spend all day on the bay.  You know why?  Cause I READ!  JUST READ!!!!!!!  READ!!!!  I was looking for the same thing you were, and didn't waste my precious bandwidth downloading something I couldn't understand!

Hope you downloaded Rosetta Stone so you could understand your prize, you tool.  

Get bent.
